title: "C4 Code Level: LangGraph Flow — ИИ Архитектор Retry Loop"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> retrieve_patterns: START

    retrieve_patterns --> select_patterns: retrieved_patterns (top-K)

    select_patterns --> design_components: selected_patterns + primary_pattern

    state retry_zone {
        design_components --> design_integrations: components[]
        design_integrations --> synthesize_diagram: data_flows[]
        synthesize_diagram --> validate_architecture: mermaid_diagram + yaml_spec
    }

    validate_architecture --> [*]: approved (score >= 0.7)
    validate_architecture --> design_components: retry (iter < MAX_RETRIES)\nfeedback → feedback_history
    validate_architecture --> [*]: max_retries (iter >= MAX_RETRIES)

    note right of retrieve_patterns
        RAG: Qdrant similarity search
        Выполняется ОДИН РАЗ
    end note

    note right of select_patterns
        LLM: PatternSelection schema
        Выполняется ОДИН РАЗ
    end note

    note right of design_components
        LLM: ComponentList schema
        RETRYABLE с feedback_history
    end note

    note right of synthesize_diagram
        Python: детерминированный
        БЕЗ LLM
    end note

    note right of validate_architecture
        LLM: ValidationOutput schema
        4 критерия → score → approved/retry
    end note
